code: @Override public boolean matches(int pathIndex, PathPattern.MatchingContext matchingContext) {     // If there is more data, it must start with the separator     if (pathIndex < matchingContext.pathLength && !matchingContext.isSeparator(pathIndex)) {         return false.     }     if (matchingContext.determineRemainingPath) {         matchingContext.remainingPathIndex = matchingContext.pathLength.     }     return true. }
